{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cd797080da","title":"对孤守工厂区敌军可劝降以减少破坏","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"898c6c58a8","index":0,"year":1949,"month":1,"day":6,"articleId":"cd797080da"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33fb58836d","type":"paragraph","text":"对孤守工厂区敌军可劝降以减少破坏","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"cd797080da"},{"id":"45237cff87","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年1月6日）林、谭：子微电邮器。（一）刘亚楼所提三条是正确的。（二）我们所顾虑的是工厂区，如果敌人占据工厂顽抗，我军必须歼灾该敌，即使工广有所破环也不要顾情。但是，如果关津其他地域的故军均已解决，仅剩下工厂区的故军而又有可能采用劝降方法解决，则应试图采用动隆方法，以便减少被坏。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"cd797080da"},{"id":"43acbf37a5","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"cd797080da"},{"id":"d34835056f","type":"paragraph","text":"鱼丑[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央平委起草的给东北野战军司令员林范和政治[2]指1949年1月5日林息、课政给中共中央军委的电报。电报同意刘外国国旗的情况提出解决这一同题的三点意见：（一）敌人已加以设防并据以位置实行监视。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"cd797080da"}],"page":{"id":"abcbfb6ded","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"cd797080da","start":502,"end":502}}}},"__N_SSG":true}